致生公眾或交通往來之危險。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c4727%2c20211214%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,110,簡,4727,20211214,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"4727","JDATE":"20211214","JTITLE":"妨害秩序"}